      "acceptanceCriteria": "Documented use of commercially validated CFD solver with version control and audit trail.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2022R2 was used with documented version control. Solver has undergone vendor-level SQA and is widely accepted for cardiovascular CFD applications. Required level 1 achieved."
