      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver passes standard benchmark verification cases relevant to rotating machinery flow.",
      "rationale": "The commercial solver has been verified against standard CFD benchmark cases including lid-driven cavity and rotating channel flows. Vendor verification documentation reviewed and found adequate for MRL 2."
