      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoI (relative hemolysis index RH) directly addresses the clinical decision criterion.",
      "rationale": "The relative hemolysis index RH compares the device under test against the predicate device. This QoI is directly linked to the regulatory acceptance criterion (RH < 1) and is clinically meaningful for CPB hemolysis risk assessment. Required level 2 satisfied."
    },
